/* warning before accessing private files */
"Some folders which will be scanned contain private files. The access is protected by the macOS privacy protection.\n\nUpon first access macOS will ask whether you allow Disk Inventory Z access to these folders and files.\n\nDisk Inventory Z does not read any data - just information like file sizes and types are collected." =
